{"tid":785804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【月光族】年輕人裝身+打機+食=成份糧　「我唔會儲錢，除非要買嘢。」","createTime":"2018-08-19T13:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T15:46:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8feeb497ac3464cea79f25a6acb7967c5221e68a","tid":785804,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:20:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20180819/20479675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F20479675&d=1lCqc%2Bpq6fJsAPOhlIaZW10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c9713393\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F20479675&h=bb44c947\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20180819/20479675</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【月光族】年輕人裝身+打機+食=成份糧　「我唔會儲錢，除非要買嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180819/large/19sub491n02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180819%2Flarge%2F19sub491n02.jpg&h=999f132b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民趁糧盡前大肆購物。<br />\n<br />\n年輕一代的理財觀念前衞，他們趁早享受財務自由（不儲蓄地生活），然後（可能）才開始建立儲蓄習慣。無論男女，他們主要花費在衣物上，其次是鞋子。課金及享受美食的比重亦佔不少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180819/large/19sub491n03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180819%2Flarge%2F19sub491n03.jpg&h=553513b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受訪者發現自己沒有儲蓄習慣而表示驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由花費習慣可見，年輕一代的餘暇生活是圍繞裝身、打機及吃，過着幸福快樂的日子。<br />\n<br />\n製作︰怪奇<br />\n<br />\n即Like全新飲食專頁【籽想好食】：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/food.appleseed/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffood.appleseed%2F&d=1lCqc%2Bpq6fJsAPOhlIaZW10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=5e83ce52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/food.appleseed/</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【果籽人話】月光族自白　指揮家財散人安樂活在當下<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【越陌度阡】愛蓮"},{"pid":"65ba3066e191f6b8ebbf8363d85e5326c302a538","tid":785804,"uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"踩港撚 分化撚將全面進場"},{"pid":"caf8b933afa86446885b8a9c6d3444b664f77087","tid":785804,"uid":28563,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:33:58.000Z","msg":"唔通儲40年當150尺樓首期？"},{"pid":"a2948b8378c77991c2b54fee680f8e6e40251c99","tid":785804,"uid":169310,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:11:43.000Z","msg":"香港買樓根本on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 衣食住行本身就係人權，你會唔會用成世勞工力去買衫著，本身應該大家都有，香港變左投資工具"},{"pid":"c9e14c404aba7932a6049481b69f85e8be6a5092","tid":785804,"uid":126256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"儲左又點<br />\n物價升得快過火箭"},{"pid":"31151a22caa872d48ee25c50dd283733a4bbfc52","tid":785804,"uid":159577,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9e14c404aba7932a6049481b69f85e8be6a5092","tid":785804,"uid":126256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"儲左又點<br />\n物價升得快過火箭"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:50:41.000Z","msg":"儲左之後就可以諗點樣資產增值，唔儲就乜都唔駛諗<br />\n<br />\n同埋經濟總有起落，經濟差股市跌樓市跌時，儲到舊錢嗰個未必一定贏，但機會一定高過冇錢嗰個"},{"pid":"ac91351e345b38ec37b9be7c3fe0b7684b0d9a28","tid":785804,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T14:51:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3173afdea70c3779b17a38c6c14aa6c857e92335","tid":785804,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:08:16.000Z","msg":"唔洗落自己度<br />\n<br />\n唔通比大商家？"},{"pid":"47cee27b1f7cdc1b722a8d06da032521f41e8a32",